  "detailed_description": "Knockback Knockout is a 2D online party game where 2-6 players compete in various game modes to claim bragging rights as the ultimate champion.<br><br>But there’s a twist…<br>This is not a traditional shooter - you must use your weapon to not only shoot at other players, but also to make your way around the map using recoil mechanics!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197430/extras/20aeff0c41ec106640e8f3dea804fd4c.webp?t=1698150507\" width=8 height=8 /></span>  Invite your friends and challenge them to various game modes - some you've heard of, some new:<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197430/extras/20aeff0c41ec106640e8f3dea804fd4c.webp?t=1698150507\" width=8 height=8 /></span>  Solo game modes:</ul></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197430/extras/15475d3ca0fba398bfba42f69a4e5ec8.webp?t=1698150507\" width=8 height=8 /></span>  Deathmatch</ul></ul></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197430/extras/15475d3ca0fba398bfba42f69a4e5ec8.webp?t=1698150507\" width=8 height=8 /></span>  Floor is Lava</ul></ul></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197430/extras/15475d3ca0fba398bfba42f69a4e5ec8.webp?t=1698150507\" width=8 height=8 /></span>  Recoil Race</ul></ul></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"